  "detailed_description": "Battle through the stars defending your space station against waves of merciless enemies in this challenging tower defense /  real time strategy hybrid. Defend the station at all costs against a ruthless foe that learns from your strategy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/9627c773ac8802578b94ae756d2e7d3a.avif?t=1725035993\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br>Enemy path updates based on your defense strategy.<br>Master the pathing to bend your foe to your will, but don't get comfortable!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/fdef541c8cec7bb8a82b3ec344cb46eb.poster.avif?t=1725035993\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/fdef541c8cec7bb8a82b3ec344cb46eb.webm?t=1725035993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/fdef541c8cec7bb8a82b3ec344cb46eb.mp4?t=1725035993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/c63abeb7e6db9834ce83fc570db821d2.avif?t=1725035993\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Customize each Ship to maximize efficiency!<br></li><li>Leverage the strengths of each turret type to dominate your foe!<br></li><li>Deploy powerfull structures to secure your victory!!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/135f6a9d2643cfd08ec96b2668b57e29.poster.avif?t=1725035993\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/135f6a9d2643cfd08ec96b2668b57e29.webm?t=1725035993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/135f6a9d2643cfd08ec96b2668b57e29.mp4?t=1725035993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/6e103729d5cef5ff00fd6c24b2a1f428.avif?t=1725035993\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Move your ships to their optimal location!<br></li><li>Command entire wings of ships at one time!<br></li><li>Level up your units with veterancy skills to fit your playstyle!</li></ul></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/4cab34047230fb746628df1ced9fa606.poster.avif?t=1725035993\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/4cab34047230fb746628df1ced9fa606.webm?t=1725035993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/4cab34047230fb746628df1ced9fa606.mp4?t=1725035993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/ed29574fdbfd421f8d7761703299fd0b.avif?t=1725035993\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>15 Unique Levels<br></li><li>Challenging system effects to test even the most strategic minds<br></li><li>Modified wave progression for each level</li></ul></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/20a1f820a445d450df31fb609320a065.poster.avif?t=1725035993\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/20a1f820a445d450df31fb609320a065.webm?t=1725035993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/20a1f820a445d450df31fb609320a065.mp4?t=1725035993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/71bb05a540cb6054bb447e25ea8f7f2e.avif?t=1725035993\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Upgrade Each ship how you want to use it!<br></li><li>Upgrade the Weapons systems you want to use with powerful capstone upgrades!<br></li><li>Upgrade your station for survivability and income!<br></li><li>Each wave defeated grants a new upgrade point to strengthen your fleet!</li></ul></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/ba4d44ffce7380dee99ef5a192e9a4c9.poster.avif?t=1725035993\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/ba4d44ffce7380dee99ef5a192e9a4c9.webm?t=1725035993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300690/extras/ba4d44ffce7380dee99ef5a192e9a4c9.mp4?t=1725035993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
